OL,3,CThames Water delays challenging
OL,4,Cwatchdog's ruling on bills amid rescue
OL,5,Cplan
OL,7,FThames Water has agreed to delay a
OL,8,Fpossible appeal over how much it can
OL,9,Fcharge for customer bills while talks
OL,10,Fover a refinancing deal with potential
OL,11,Fbuyers take place.
OL,13,FThe UK's biggest water firm, whose UK
OL,14,Fheadquarters are in Reading,
OL,15,FBerkshire, said it had agreed with
OL,16,FOfwat to defer the case until further
OL,17,Fnotice.
