OL,3,CThames Water delays challenging
OL,4,Cwatchdog's ruling on bills amid rescue
OL,5,Cplan
OL,7,FIt had previously asked the water
OL,8,Fwatchdog to refer its price review to
OL,9,Fthe UK's Competition and Markets
OL,10,FAuthority (CMA).
OL,12,FIt is among a number of utilities
OL,13,Ffirms urging regulators to allow them
OL,14,Fto charge customers more for bills
OL,15,Fthan previously granted, having argued
OL,16,Fthat what was allowed by Ofwat was not
OL,17,Fenough to support investment and
OL,18,Fimprovement plans.
