OL,5,Cplan
OL,7,FDoing so was "in the interests of our
OL,8,Fcustomers and the environment", Thames
OL,9,Fsaid in February.
OL,11,FDeferring the potential appeal comes
OL,12,Fafter a group of its investors offered
OL,13,Fa rescue deal for the troubled utility
OL,14,Ffirm.
