OL,7,FA spokesman for Ofwat said: "Thames
OL,8,FWater has requested a further deferral
OL,9,Fof its 2024 Price Review final
OL,10,Fdetermination reference to the
OL,11,FCompetition and Markets Authority
OL,12,F(CMA).
OL,14,F"Given the ongoing discussions with
OL,15,Fthe company's creditors, Ofwat has
OL,16,Fagreed to this request and informed
OL,17,Fthe CMA.
